
Image(Davisconsumers_2.png)The DavisConsumers is a locally owned website that pools and summarizes coupons, deals, jobs, and weekly Ad specials offered by Davis and nearby community businesses. Unlike many other websites that pursue omnibearing coverage but finally become information maze, DavisConsumers keeps in small size and concise mode. Just a click, consumers can gain a comprehensive overview of discounts and freebies in Davis and nearby communities, enjoy fresh products, excellent goods, and quality services offered by local businesses at low price  saving them both time and money!

